quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  53,27,Achiika! Ninvuɣu shεba ban bi tiri Chiyaama yεlimaŋli maa n-nyɛ ban mali Malaaikanim’ boondi paɣaba la
  53,28,"Bɛ mi ka di baŋsim shεli, bɛ bi doli shɛli m-pahila zilsigu, zilsigu mi ku tooi zani yɛlimaŋli zaa ni n-niŋ anfaani shɛli"
  53,29,"Dinzuɣu (yaa nyini Annabi)! Yim ninvuɣu so ŋun lebi biri Ti (Tinim’ Naawuni) yɛla teebu, ka bi bɔri shεli naɣila Dunia biεhigu"
  53,30,Dina n-nyɛ bɛ (chɛfurinim’) baŋsim targi. Achiika! A Duuma (Naawuni) n-nyɛ Ŋun mi ninvuɣu so ŋun bɔrgi ka chɛ O soli. Ŋuna n-lahi mi ŋun dolsi
  53,31,"Yaha! Naawuni n-su din be sagbana ni, ni din be tiŋgbani ni. Achiika! O (Naawuni) nyɛla Ŋun yɛn ti yo ninvuɣu shεba ban tum tuumbiεri samli ka di saɣisi bɛ ni tum shɛli, ka yo ban tum tuunviεla ni sanyoviεlli (Alizanda)"
  53,32,"Ninvuɣu shεba ban ŋindi katiŋ’ ka chɛri tuumbekara, n-ti pahi kavituma, naɣila taali bihi. Achiika! A Duuma (Naawuni) nyɛla Ŋun chε m-paŋ galsi, Ŋuna n-nyɛ Ŋun mi hali shεŋa ni yi ni be saha shεli O ni yihi ya tiŋgbani yaaŋa zuɣu na, ni saha shεli yi ni daa nyɛ bilεri yi manim’ puya ni. Dinzuɣu, miri ya ka yi simsiri yi maŋa, Ŋuna m mi ninvuɣu so ŋun mali wuntia"
  53,33,(Yaa nyini Annabi)! A nya ninvuɣu so ŋun lebi biri
  53,34,"Ka ti pini bɛla, ka lahi niŋ biɛm"
  53,35,"Di ni bɔŋɔ, o malila din sɔɣi baŋsim, ka nyɛla ŋun shiri nyara"
  53,36,Bee bɛ bi ti o la din be Annabi Musa kundili (litaafi) puuni lahibali
  53,37,Ni Annabi Ibrahima so ŋun daa pali alikauli la
  53,38,Kadama nyɛvuli shεli din mali taali ku tooi deei di nyɛvuli kpee taali ʒi
  53,39,Yaha! Ninsala ti ka shɛli (Zaadali) naɣila o ni daa tum shɛli (Dunia)
  53,40,"Yaha! Achiika! Ni baalim, bɛ ni ti nya o tuma ni daa nyɛ shɛli (Zaadali)"
  53,41,"Din nyaaŋa, bɛ ni yo o samli, ka di nyɛ sanyo’ shɛli din pali"
  53,42,Yaha! Achiika! A Duuma sani n- nyɛ bahigu shee
  53,43,"Yaha! Achiika! Ŋuna n-nyɛ Ŋun chɛ ka ninvuɣu so lara, ka chɛ ka so mi kuhira"
  53,44,"Yaha! Achiika! Ŋuna n-nyɛ Ŋun kura, ka neera"